<topic id='business_definition_healthcare_resource_group_unbundled_activity.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Healthcare Resource Group Unbundled Activity - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_healthcare_resource_group_unbundled_activity">Healthcare Resource Group Unbundled Activity</xref>
 identifies separate elements of cost and 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>
 from the core 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_healthcare_resource_group">Healthcare Resource Group</xref>, and are generated in addition to the core 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_healthcare_resource_group">Healthcare Resource Group</xref>
 for an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>, episode or spell of care or attendance.        </p>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_healthcare_resource_group_unbundled_activity">Healthcare Resource Group Unbundled Activity</xref>
 may be event based and derived from a specific 
              <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_opcs-4_code">OPCS-4 CODE</xref>
 in the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 record, or duration based. Multiple 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_healthcare_resource_group_unbundled_activity">Healthcare Resource Group Unbundled Activities</xref>
 may be generated in addition to a single core 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_healthcare_resource_group">Healthcare Resource Group</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
For further information on 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_healthcare_resource_group">Healthcare Resource Groups</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/services/national-casemix-office/downloads-groupers-and-tools" scope="external" format="html">Downloads - Groupers and Tools</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
